      Z\ar [r, "c"]\ar [d, "b"'] & C\ar [d, "g"] \\
      B\ar [r, "f"'] & A\makebox [0pt][l]{,}
    \end {tikzcd}


there exists a unique morphism Z\to  P making the following diagram
  commute:





